      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Open a repository-stored graph\n\n1. Copy its `github://` address.\n2. Paste the address into Twilite’s browser bar.\n3. Press Enter.\n4. Follow portals normally; Twilite keeps GitHub addresses as GitHub addresses.\n\nExample: `github://mikemartinez1974/public/root.node`",
        "identity": {
          "graphId": "github-guide"
        }
      }
    },
