        "markdown": "## Edit and save intentionally\n\n1. Open the repository-stored graph.\n2. Enter edit mode and make the change.\n3. Confirm the save destination: owner, repository, branch, and path.\n4. Save through the connected GitHub authority.\n5. Treat conflicts as revision conflicts—do not silently overwrite newer work.",
