        "markdown": "## Read the interface before writing\n\n- **Document** identifies what is open.\n- **Save target** identifies where the next write will go.\n- **Access** identifies the GitHub installation being used.\n\nThe open graph and the next save destination are related, but they should never be assumed to be identical.",
